name: Tokee - Crypto Community App
description:
In Tokee - Crypto Community App file you can find advanced search bar transition, hamburger menu icon micro-interaction alongside tiles introduction and graphs reveal. Moreover, you can see the custom voice search animation and some more.


This is only an example, showcasing what can be done in Figma using auto animate. Use it whether as a reference or copy & paste it into your prototypes.


Enjoy!
